title: COAST / GARY barks coast
description: Things Gary says on the coast.

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""Lots of people out there miss the..."
dialogueTree.english: "Lots of people out there miss the good old days."

dialogueTree.belarusian: «Шмат людзей сумуе па старых добрых часах».

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""People are starting to think, waki..."
dialogueTree.english: "People are starting to think, waking up."

dialogueTree.belarusian: «Хто не марыў пра тое, каб Хельмдаль было сапраўдным месцам?»

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""You think it's gonna be much longe..."
dialogueTree.english: "You think it's gonna be much longer?"

dialogueTree.english: "People are just scared of the truth."

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""I'm just saying, as a *Revacholian..."
dialogueTree.english: "I'm just saying, as a *Revacholian*, I am slightly worried."
